      "decision": "P2: Move background jobs to proper job queue infrastructure",
      "gains": "Built-in retry, backpressure, monitoring, no HTTP timeout risk, proper concurrency control, dead-letter queues",
      "sacrifices": "New infrastructure dependency, migration effort, need to re-implement job monitoring",
