      "decision": "P1: Replace Reporting Service direct DB reads with dedicated read model",
      "gains": "Order Service can evolve schema freely, Reporting gets optimized read model, no cross-service query performance impact",
      "sacrifices": "Data staleness (seconds to minutes), additional infrastructure for event streaming or CDC, initial build effort for read model",
      "alternatives_considered": ["Database read replica with restricted access (easy but still couples on schema)", "API-based data access from Reporting to Order Service (simple but poor for bulk analytics queries)"]
