      "risk": "Shared Order/Courier database allows cascading failures: a bad migration in Courier can lock Order tables, a connection pool exhaustion in one affects both",
      "severity": "critical",
      "mitigation": "P0 — Split into separate database instances with dual-write migration strategy; use Change Data Capture during transition"
