      "The /everything endpoint is consumed by multiple different services with different data needs, not just a single frontend",
      "The cron-over-HTTP background jobs do not have idempotency guards, making duplicate execution a real risk",
      "The organization has the infrastructure capability to operate a message broker and potentially a CDC tool"
    ]
  }
